{"tid":1892684,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦網絡問題","createTime":"2020-02-22T16:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T14:15:56.000Z","uid":103558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70cfc539679caec1bb1c13b4fb8fda87cec6eb57","tid":1892684,"uid":103558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"我電腦用lan線直插，另外有一個router放WiFi<br />\n之前一直都正常用緊。<br />\n近排有個問題就係 佢地唔可以一齊上到網<br />\n我電腦連到線，個WiFi 就用唔到 <br />\n個wifi上到，就到電腦冇ip<br />\n打過去網上行問，佢話兩樣野係到搶ip<br />\n試左用wifi手指插落電腦，但係比用lan線慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知道有冇方法可以我電腦直插lan線又用到，個router又正常用到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電腦：win10<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題係呢個月先發生 之前都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7413ffd5235d9a9bb486dae3207614ce08a0886","tid":1892684,"uid":271120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"轉個2x1000咪解決到囉"},{"pid":"f6af32750ee65519b5181e1da9420f6bc3d3f3b3","tid":1892684,"uid":267331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"撞IP"},{"pid":"3722b98d803caf3e5af7417cb99f094a4a5f7996","tid":1892684,"uid":103558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7413ffd5235d9a9bb486dae3207614ce08a0886","tid":1892684,"uid":271120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"轉個2x1000咪解決到囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 唔係好識 姐係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd3197f1f9ec43767e8185483a49a6bea39a527","tid":1892684,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"我TeamViewer幫你睇下?"},{"pid":"add64e792649aa15264986fc45c3143c8e55c2d5","tid":1892684,"uid":271120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3722b98d803caf3e5af7417cb99f094a4a5f7996","tid":1892684,"uid":103558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7413ffd5235d9a9bb486dae3207614ce08a0886","tid":1892684,"uid":271120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"轉個2x1000咪解決到囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 唔係好識 姐係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"網上行有啲2x1000mb plan 一條直入元朗 一條入wife 🤟🏻"},{"pid":"d88bcdac023a0cc8838a62ec49223d4c793403d8","tid":1892684,"uid":145321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"你部PC LAN 線吉緊咩機？<br />\n入黎條Internet 又吉緊咩？<br />\n你既另一部WiFi router 又吉緊咩？ <br />\n係Win 10 Show 過ipconfig <br />\n再用手機又show 返IP 黎睇睇<br />\n<br />\n假設你有一條WAN link <br />\nWAN link fiber  -&gt; modem -&gt; RJ45 port 去你WiFi router WAN 頭-&gt; 你部WIFI router 仲有Lan 頭比你接電腦<br />\n<br />\n留意下你部PC 係咪用DHCH<br />\n上面應該fix 到你問題"},{"pid":"ebb051cd117e3e45fcccadba7b429fd585f9642c","tid":1892684,"uid":145321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d88bcdac023a0cc8838a62ec49223d4c793403d8","tid":1892684,"uid":145321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"你部PC LAN 線吉緊咩機？<br />\n入黎條Internet 又吉緊咩？<br />\n你既另一部WiFi router 又吉緊咩？ <br />\n係Win 10 Show 過ipconfig <br />\n再用手機又show 返IP 黎睇睇<br />\n<br />\n假設你有一條WAN link <br />\nWAN link fiber  -&gt; modem -&gt; RJ45 port 去你WiFi router WAN 頭-&gt; 你部WIFI router 仲有Lan 頭比你接電腦<br />\n<br />\n留意下你部PC 係咪用DHCH<br />\n上面應該fix 到你問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"DHCP"},{"pid":"8147d50de55ea515dcf1a68aec0de6789c573ab4","tid":1892684,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:41:49.000Z","msg":"你呢個情況係個modem 比你兩個相同既ip比你部電腦同router<br />\n<br />\n1. 一係就係isp唔比你用兩個ip出街 <br />\n<br />\n2. 一係部modem有問題<br />\n<br />\n解決方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 1.Modem -&gt;router -&gt; pc 呢個一定冇問題<br />\n<br />\n 1.2.或者買部switch<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n       modem -&gt; switch -&gt; router &amp; pc<br />\n       但呢個方法好on鳩<br />\n<br />\n2. 叫isp換機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 唔識"},{"pid":"84e0b1d0bfcc535b1ba7962130e87c69b43d4cda","tid":1892684,"uid":3690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:45:20.000Z","msg":"如果你係用一開二果D hubs 部電腦會搶咗個public IP 所以router上唔到網,所以你只可以靠router DHCP 派private IP比你先可以所有devices 一齊上到網"},{"pid":"3b7b16aa84521266e5ae7a0b837b47124b288942","tid":1892684,"uid":103558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"唔該曬 終於得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}